description: Vegibox Connects you with Fresh Produce
overview:
Vegibox Connects you with Fresh Produce, Locally Delivered To Your Door From The Heart of the New Forest - Choose box size & how often you want your delivery, Weekly or Fortnightly.

Today there is a growing demand with consumers seeking to understand the origin along with the journey of their everyday food.

Our Mission is to encourage locals to engage with local produce. If produce in your Vegibox is not locally grown by us or our partner farms, then at every opportunity we source for you the best available healthy products from producers within the UK who share the same ethic values as Vegibox.
